{"tid":1124945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完復仇者聯盟4被送院急救 寧波女生：哭得太傷心","createTime":"2019-04-25T10:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T11:53:29.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e63224508a6d102a9b199029e24238d7ed86795","tid":1124945,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"浙江寧波21歲女生小麗（化名），於24日凌晨看完《復仇者聯盟4》首映後，突發胸悶氣促、手指抽筋而被送院急救。經醫生診斷，小麗是因為睇電影時，哭得太傷心，一直大口喘氣，造成肺部過度通氣，血液中二氧化碳通過肺部排出的速率超過了身體產生二氧化碳的速率，造成頭暈或頭痛等。<br />\n<br />\n醫生表示，通過安撫患者令其情緒放鬆，吸氧或戴上口罩，減少換氣頻率，即可緩解症狀。<br />\n《新京報》<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190425&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59527776&amp;utm_source=url_copy&amp;utm_medium=url_copy&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190425%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59527776%26utm_source%3Durl_copy%26utm_medium%3Durl_copy%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SdXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=26b60b3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190425%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59527776%26utm_source%3Durl_copy%26utm_medium%3Durl_copy%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=704b17f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190425&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59527776&amp;utm_source=url_copy&amp;utm_medium=url_copy&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"ae66141b5e35c3aeea31a54ebfe11fe6bb67660d","tid":1124945,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"真係痴痴地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5589e07fdd1904e514bd3fab7814793eaccd8210","tid":1124945,"uid":45459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T11:52:05.000Z","msg":"哭得太傷心<img src=\"/as